  "name": "Irresistible Demand",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/ice_15.jpg",
  "sort": 0,
  "flags": {},
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 8th level, you can force others to do your bidding. As a <em>standard action</em>, you attempt to dominate a creature as though using the @Compendium[pf1.spells.66s5qm8kwycgobce]{Dominate Monster} spell, except that the creature must have a number of <em>Hit Dice</em> equal to or less than your wizard level. The targeted creature receives a <em>Will</em> <em>saving throw</em> each round to negate the effect. The DC is equal to 10 + 1/2 your wizard level + your <em>Intelligence</em> modifier. You can dominate creatures for a number of rounds per day equal to your wizard level. These rounds do not need to be consecutive. You must concentrate as a <em>standard action</em> to maintain control over a dominated creature.</p>"
    },
